IMPROVE: Spend a skill slot to raise a known skill

Syntax: improve <skill>

Spend one pending skill slot to raise a skill you already know. Each
slot adds that skill's normal per-level percentage (varies by skill,
usually +4 or +5). You earn one pending slot each time you advance a
level with the advance command.

Examples:
  improve first aid
  improve wp knife
  improve prowl

Check pending slots on score. List your skills with the skills
command.

SEE ALSO: skills, advance, score
